Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:40.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:97610,100830}It's very important to relax\Nuntil you get better from fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:41.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101060,101870}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:46.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102490,106030}You can miss another day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:106540,107870}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:50.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108120,110430}If it's only for today...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:52.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111390,112270}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:55.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112420,115000}Watch Sam well and don't let him get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117180,119660}Yes, yes, I understood, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.66,0:02:18.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136660,138450}Ah, I'm fine, Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.87,0:02:20.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138870,140740}Just feel a little bit dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.98,0:02:22.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140980,142810}What's up, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143340,145960}Ah, nothing, nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.95,0:02:29.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146950,149490}Mom, you look tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149610,151060}You also came back late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:31.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151080,151680}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.77,0:02:34.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152770,154530}All these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154550,155640}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.95,0:02:38.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:155950,158180}I'm just a bit tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:39.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:158550,159770}But, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159950,161690}I have lots of patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.71,0:02:42.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161710,162980}I need strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165010,167680}I'm really fine, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:49.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167930,169680}Please take care of your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:51.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170190,171280}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171310,172020}{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:54.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173370,174520}Melissa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175010,178980}I apologize but can you come later\Nto check on my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:00.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179370,180980}Hasn't his temperature dropped yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:01.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181040,181700}{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181890,183030}Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184350,185610}Oh, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186220,187730}How is your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:09.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187950,189300}Thank you for your concern!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191920,194150}Ah, are you still going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:15.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194170,195180}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:16.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195270,196490}Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.25,0:03:23.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200250,203840}My God, my God, it's rare\Nto be treated so harshly!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.22,0:03:24.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204220,204790}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.82,0:03:25.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204820,205930}Did you finish eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205930,207350}Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208050,211790}Many people have had cough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:33.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211970,213740}John... listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:34.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213830,214480}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.66,0:03:36.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214660,216640}{\i1}Your mother is busy these days, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217020,217650}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:39.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217670,219880}She's works too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.91,0:03:45.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219910,225580}At these times you will be busy eating lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225780,228040}{\i1}Yes, fever is rampant anyway...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.07,0:03:51.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228070,231370}{\i1}But it's bad for her not to eat lunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:52.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231810,232550}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232580,233480}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:56.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233590,236440}I'll bring the lunch to my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:59.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236690,239740}Ah, I feel fine now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239830,241550}Well, if that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.58,0:04:02.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241580,242650}Let's go, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.43,0:04:06.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244430,246040}I'm fine, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.09,0:04:07.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246090,247650}I will rest in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251060,252290}And now go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.33,0:04:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255330,259170}Yes, this time I can help my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262080,263120}{\i1}Hello!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:24.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263120,264410}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:25.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264890,265550}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266260,267710}It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267910,270570}It was very busy, but the place is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270660,271770}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:37.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276780,277950}List of patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:39.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278260,279160}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.35,0:04:41.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279350,281230}No more patient visits yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.46,0:04:48.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287460,288400}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288430,289100}Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:51.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290310,291720}- Oh!\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:54.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292720,294400}Mother, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:57.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294480,297770}I count on you to bring it\Nto the last floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:11.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309130,311430}And now won't hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311510,312920}I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312920,314510}But you should be cured of fever immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:317030,318250}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318270,320250}Still, I want you to visit us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.35,0:05:21.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320350,321220}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:23.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321300,323000}- You'll get better quickly!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323750,326120}Now, let's get to the next house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:28.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326640,328140}Busy! Busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:35.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332880,335070}The pulse...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:38.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335960,338520}Well, that way the heat will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338660,341160}Don't worry, rest only!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.18,0:05:41.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341180,341860}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:43.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342030,343440}- Here!\N- Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:47.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344180,347360}No, that's at least I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347630,349910}But... my mom and the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354460,355490}{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.76,0:05:57.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356760,357720}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.78,0:06:00.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:357780,360530}You forgot to take your lunch with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:01.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361260,361960}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:08.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365860,368560}Well, we'll be back here at five o'clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:11.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368560,371900}I must prepare medicines to\Nsend them to patients in need!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372010,373390}This is tiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:17.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375430,377590}{\i1}All the people of this house are sick!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:20.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379040,380730}{\i1}Sorry, how is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.24,0:06:23.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383240,383970}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384650,386660}Yeah, it's a little high.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386800,388350}What about Jake?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:32.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388460,392150}The father who was in this\Nhouse treated him first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394110,396590}So you'll get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:37.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396740,397540}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:42.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397640,402160}But we don't have enough fever medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:43.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402220,403210}Yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404340,406810}Yesterday I ordered other medicines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407070,408690}Maybe it won't arrive quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:52.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:408970,412590}As recently as his students didn't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:55.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412760,415590}Maybe it will arrive tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:06:57.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416120,417350}From here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418020,419860}I will go and bring it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:02.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421450,422070}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422100,423080}Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:04.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423270,424810}Hey, she fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:06.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425440,426240}{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426730,428430}{\i1}Mom! Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.98,0:07:16.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434980,436070}{\i1}Mom!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:21.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440640,441610}John...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:24.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443090,444360}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444690,445880}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:27.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:446050,447880}No, I'm the one who should apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.98,0:07:31.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447980,451090}I made you work so hard that it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451200,453010}No, I will wake up immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.08,0:07:34.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453080,454200}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:36.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455410,456840}I'm fine, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457160,458980}I'm just a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:41.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459430,461240}Patients are waiting for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.24,0:07:43.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:461240,463530}Mom, your temperature is too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.60,0:07:44.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463600,464990}{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.94,0:07:48.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:465940,468590}This is a medicine for fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:469140,470520}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:51.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470700,471930}This medicine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.02,0:07:53.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472020,473440}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473580,476720}It's normal for patients with fever\Nto receive injection!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:08:00.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476810,480060}But the drugs will be delayed\Nuntil tomorrow afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480250,481910}Not until after the dawn of tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481970,484720}Mr. Rice went to pick it up by truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:08.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484810,488110}You can inject this medicine\Nafter the medication arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488240,489360}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:12.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489460,492370}In any case, I never want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:15.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492690,495030}The other patients need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495280,496550}Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:19.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496880,499910}Your stubbornness won't be\Nas effective today as yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500000,501510}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:22.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502130,502770}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.07,0:08:24.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503070,504020}{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:26.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:504750,506470}Sam, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506500,508190}- Go to the front!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:40.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516860,520420}We've heard that Mrs. Melissa\Nhas fallen unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:41.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520620,521710}Oh... Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.76,0:08:42.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521760,522850}Please enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.17,0:08:59.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535170,539470}I made soup for you,\Nso eat it and get better quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539490,543010}Melissa, everyone knows\Nyou're concerned about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:06.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543150,546280}So everyone in the village appreciates it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546950,548430}{\i1}Yeah! Yeah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:10.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549100,550320}Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:14.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552880,554100}Melissa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554530,556110}Y--yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:19.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557240,559440}Everyone is in trouble now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:25.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559560,565520}In the village there is one nurse,\Nshe worked hard until she fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:31.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:567010,571480}Grandma, don't say that,\Nyou better appreciate her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:32.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571510,572460}Mrs. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:35.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:572810,575530}Aren't the words of Grandma Forrest true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:39.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575560,579270}It's better for you to get an injection to get\Nbetter, it's the desire of the people as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:40.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579350,580760}- Doctor!\N- That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:45.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580840,585140}While you are at home, Mom,\NI will help Dr. Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:45.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585310,585880}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586320,587010}John...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:50.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589250,590850}Lassie too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:54.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591280,594750}I don't know what the syringe is,\Nbut you have to get better soon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594780,597520}there's no one in your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597540,598440}Mhm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.09,0:10:01.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600090,601460}I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.01,0:10:13.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609010,613280}My mother worked hard for everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:15.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:613340,615280}Yes! That's right, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615510,616240}{\i1}Well...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617440,619550}I'll leave your wife to you, Sam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:20.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619720,620930}{\i1}Y-yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624480,626000}Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:26.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626020,626740}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:29.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627080,629840}Doctor, I mentioned earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:30.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629940,630500}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:31.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630530,631970}I want to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.26,0:10:33.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632260,633690}Help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:36.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633960,636610}It's hard for you, doctor,\Nto work alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:41.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636680,641010}I'm not as good as my mother,\Nbut can't I help you with a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.81,0:10:43.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641810,643330}Look, even Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:44.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643850,644560}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644680,646250}Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:49.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646330,649140}My mother was taking care of the patients too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:649260,650330}And I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651470,652360}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:55.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652520,655670}I count on you, John! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:56.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655890,656670}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.11,0:11:06.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664110,666640}Well, the lungs are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:08.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666920,668350}{\i1}John, the tongue inhibitor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.35,0:11:10.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668350,670250}Tongue inhibitor... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670270,670880}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:12.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:671220,672530}Say "a"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675000,676460}{\i1}- Laryngoscopy!{\i0}\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:18.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677560,678870}Yes, is that the binoculars?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:19.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679090,679680}{\i1}Hm!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:20.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679940,680990}{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681050,682590}Yes! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.96,0:11:24.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682960,684950}You've got the tool names, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:25.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685060,685840}Who is next?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:28.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685860,688220}No 21, Mrs. Harrison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:28.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:688310,688920}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:33.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692950,693880}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:34.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693910,694740}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694760,696060}Please get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696500,698310}We still have a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:42.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:701340,702380}{\i1}Oh my God, my God!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702590,705200}{\i1}The number of medicines is many\Nand can't be counted!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:47.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705300,707270}Now I will deliver the next medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.86,0:11:49.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707860,709320}Yes, I count on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709430,711990}I will check the inventory now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:52.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712020,712790}{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.34,0:11:57.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713340,717080}Even if his temperature is low, he is\Nstill a person to be warned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717220,720970}The man with fever never changes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:04.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721260,724910}Rice went to get the medicines,\NI hope he will return quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:13.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732270,733350}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.38,0:12:14.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733380,734920}I have to go back to the village quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734920,736800}That way I will never move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.37,0:12:20.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737370,740940}That's why I hate the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:25.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743660,745330}It's Dr. Hooper's medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:26.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745350,746010}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:28.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746230,748480}Good, there's only one house left!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:31.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750180,751400}Mr. Gabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755650,757030}Mr. Gabel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.03,0:12:38.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757030,758520}{\i1}Shut up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758550,760020}{\i1}Open the door and come in!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:42.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760430,762290}I can't let you in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766160,767110}Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767220,768920}I brought your medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769030,771420}A child? What happened to Melissa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.56,0:12:54.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771560,774990}My mother is very sick,\Nthat's why I came instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:775010,776100}{\i1}I'm here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.13,0:13:00.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778130,780860}It's different from the usual\Nrheumatoid medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:02.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780890,782080}It's a fever medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782170,783960}Please eat your full food!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:04.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783980,784500}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.67,0:13:06.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784670,786010}Well, I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:06.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786030,786960}{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:787220,788810}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:12.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789020,792030}Even food can't be eaten, as you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792120,794250}I can't move from bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795100,796250}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796560,799460}You ask me to make food for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:20.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799500,800390}That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800470,802690}I can't take this medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802710,803490}Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.35,0:13:25.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804350,805230}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.56,0:13:26.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805560,806950}It's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806980,808570}I have to start by washing dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808700,810470}I don't have any pot to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810580,812010}Do you have any complaint?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:34.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812110,814410}Melissa always does that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814580,815530}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816080,817160}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.68,0:13:41.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818680,821410}Mom, do this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.92,0:13:45.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824920,825830}I have finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826260,828140}Well, I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828160,829150}{\i1}Wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:52.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831650,832620}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:56.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833520,836220}I hope you always come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.67,0:13:58.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836670,838920}{\i1}You do this well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:13:59.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839040,839840}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.17,0:14:03.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840170,843250}I will ask you to do so from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846780,847450}Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849230,850480}Dr. Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:11.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850620,851890}He's walking fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852640,854510}What? What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854740,857330}Mr. Gabel, I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857500,859920}I think Dr. Hooper has many patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.30,0:14:21.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860300,861640}Wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861790,864470}I'm sorry, but I really have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864580,865760}xxx!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:28.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:865880,868690}If you open the cabinet\Nyou will find a bottle shelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868900,870610}{\i1}It's the special strawberry drink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:33.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870700,873380}{\i1}It have been very helpful to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:35.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873460,875900}{\i1}That's why I should give Melissa this drink.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:41.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:876640,881830}{\i1}Melissa always looked after me\Nwithout grumbling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.98,0:14:43.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:881980,883660}Thank you, Mr. Gabel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883790,885960}I... I will come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890230,891430}Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891700,892800}Oh, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892850,895410}Jake's temperature has risen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896140,897830}Ah, this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:02.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:900390,902780}It was worse because we weren't careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.39,0:15:06.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905390,906340}Aunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:906980,909940}Is Jake okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:13.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910090,913340}What? He don't have pneumonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.45,0:15:16.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913450,916440}If it doesn't get to the point he will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:18.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916560,918880}Well... I will take care of him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.66,0:15:21.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919660,921950}Aunt, you have to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:22.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922160,922980}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:25.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923480,925870}I will take care of Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:28.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925960,928410}Aunt, you have to recover your health quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:30.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:928880,930070}But this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930070,933710}When you get well, Auntie,\Nyou can take care of Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933950,935240}Isn't it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935380,936450}{\i1}Right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937040,939200}Now go back to your bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:42.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939420,942280}Tomorrow morning when you recover
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942300,944950}you can hug Jake as much as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:45.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945060,945740}Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:54.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953990,954750}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955000,956700}How is his temperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.91,0:15:57.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956910,957540}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957660,960750}The temperature is high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960850,962760}Still high?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:962850,963430}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:07.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963580,967250}Well, it's just a fever,\Nso there's no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967870,970510}His temperature can decrease\Nif we observe it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.60,0:16:13.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970600,973270}We must wait for Rice to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:19.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978540,979700}{\i1}Damn!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979720,982060}It broke at such a time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982770,984700}I have a lot of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986160,987670}The medicine hasn't arrived yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987700,988940}{\i1}Doctor Hooper!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.97,0:16:29.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988970,989540}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.60,0:16:32.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989600,992560}I went to the clinic and found the paper\Nwhere you wrote that you are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:992690,993570}What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.14,0:16:36.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994140,996830}My mother's fever has increased again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.95,0:16:38.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996950,998740}Please take a look at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:42.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999280,1002040}That's all. I have to go to Olsen's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:45.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002210,1005450}I apologize but please take good care of Jake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:49.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005820,1009730}If his temperature suddenly rises,\Ntell me immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.98,0:16:50.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009980,1010730}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.38,0:16:54.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011380,1014270}Ah, also don't forget to dry the towel again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.46,0:16:56.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014460,1016420}- Yes, Doctor!\N- Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:00.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018850,1020060}Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:06.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024150,1026840}Let's do our best... Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:14.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032810,1034640}I am thirsty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035460,1036990}Do you feel thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.21,0:17:18.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037210,1038080}Do you want water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.19,0:17:18.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038190,1038790}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.07,0:17:19.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039070,1039910}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:27.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046800,1047500}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056490,1058330}Well, sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058440,1060720}I will turn off the light now\Nso don't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.93,0:17:50.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069930,1070650}{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:52.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070730,1072250}{\i1}He sleeps deeply.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073550,1074320}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.78,0:18:00.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076780,1080500}Even if I kept changing, it was still hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:19.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098730,1099620}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.84,0:18:22.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099840,1102160}{\i1}It's time to measure his temperature!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:25.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102600,1105220}Thank you, Lassie, for waking me up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124150,1126020}Has time passed already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:01.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140090,1141220}I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:04.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142690,1144250}It has grown again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149440,1151530}It's bad! Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152370,1154410}What to do? His temperature has risen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:16.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154620,1156270}What? What's with this blanket?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157140,1159070}What? Did you wake up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:21.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159690,1161510}Mom, is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161620,1163200}Thank you for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.38,0:19:24.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163380,1164590}By the way, Jake...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:25.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164590,1165660}Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165730,1167180}{\i1}Calm down, John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167260,1168540}He needs cooling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:30.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168700,1170480}I wish we had snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:31.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170500,1171050}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:31.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171140,1171940}Snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.13,0:19:33.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172130,1173770}Would you be okay with the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:37.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175420,1177390}Lassie, we must find snow quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177510,1179420}But where do we get it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:44.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181460,1184880}Excuse me, Mr. Nelson!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.42,0:19:48.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185420,1188460}W-what do you want at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:50.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1188630,1190820}If there is snow in your refrigerator,\Ngive it to me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190950,1192900}In the Parkinson house, it's Jake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193040,1194650}{\i1}Jake has a high temperature!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194670,1196110}What? This is a big problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.18,0:20:12.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211180,1212360}That's enough, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212380,1213870}Now he calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.94,0:20:23.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221940,1223910}If I sleep a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:27.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1224660,1227770}After an hour we'll exchange places.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228020,1229740}So Mr. Rice is back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:32.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229950,1232560}It will be a problem if the fever returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232720,1233600}Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1237720,1238380}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238570,1240190}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:45.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1244760,1245880}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.40,0:20:52.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251400,1252350}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:55.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254990,1255640}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:20:57.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255940,1257180}What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259000,1261050}{\i1}What? Do you want me to follow you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.14,0:21:03.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262140,1263220}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264260,1266000}Sorry sorry, I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:06.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266030,1266990}Doctor Hooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268020,1268870}Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:11.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269560,1271350}Hey Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.35,0:21:12.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271350,1272820}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272920,1274670}I brought medicines!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:17.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275280,1277840}Lassie is the one who brought Mr. Rice here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:21.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277950,1281100}Mom! The medicine! The medicine arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.69,0:21:23.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281690,1283050}Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.65,0:21:32.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289650,1292690}That's great, Jake, you've already recovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.71,0:21:34.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1292710,1294760}So, even you, Mom, I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1298130,1299730}{\i1}You worked hard, John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:43.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1299950,1303360}No, but you, Mom, you always\Nwork hard and always...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.69,0:21:45.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303690,1305880}Always do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.92,0:21:51.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1307920,1311670}I am proud because you are my mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.46,0:22:04.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320460,1324650}{\i1}Grandmother Forrest's son returned\Nto the village 20 years later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:08.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324680,1328470}{\i1}But the grandmother didn't reply\Nand didn't received her son.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:12.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1328720,1332220}{\i1}At that time, her grandson also appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332440,1334900}{\i1}Next episode:\NI WANT TO SEE MY GRANDMOTHER{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:16.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1334900,1336230}{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
